 dishonorable monk Kanos</span><hr size=1> Was in Sol b earlier today (EDIT* on my monk Zorraaz level 53) with my druid friend.  Called a camp check and named and BnB were camped so we decides to take Window room.  Being that I am 53 I don't get great exp in there since 50% of them are green and the rest are that light blue color.  My druid friend was only 41 one yellow from 42 so I wanted to help her get her level.<br><br>Was going really good until about 20 min after we were at the camp we both saw this monk run by us a couple times and head up into the rooms I guess looking for some spawns to kill.  So I then OOC'ed that window was camped.  Kanos ( the monk ) then OOC'ed that we should share the camp.  Now I know its nice to ask the people first to share the camp other than take it right from underneath them.<br><br>I mentioned to him that the zone is open and he should camp those ( since a soloing monk cant really hold a full window adds in wrong place).  Well he didn't want to and demanded again we share.  So knowing that I cant stop him from taking a few spawns I just went with it.  I tried to get as many of the spawns as I can before he got the agro, but he was getting some.<br><br>He once had 3 of the spawns on him and was also getting low on HP.  He asked me to take one, but I didn't want to take one cause he can call me a KSer since I took his agro,  and I was telling myself that if he gets in a bad situations and he realizes he shouldn't stay that he would leave.  Well he was only able to kill one of the 3 kobolds on him, then FDed when he was about to die and the mobs then agroed on to me.  I killed those mobs he Fded on to me and went on with the killing.<br><br>I walked up into a room and had 2 kobolds agro on me.  Without even asking if he can take one of those mobs that I can easily handle, he took the one I wasn't currently hitting but was agroed on me and KSed it before I could have outdmged him trying to KS.  I even warned him not to KS me and he did anyway.  I told him after the battle that he just KSed me and he said &quot; no I didn't, if anything you KSed me&quot;.  Well it went on and on with arguments about the situations and the Guide I called wasn't too much of a help (like they do much anyway).  He tried to tell me that me killing the 2 kobolds he FDed on me was KSing him even though he cleared his agro while FD.<br><br>But I just thought that all of you should know of this monk, He is currently Guildless (wonder why heheh ), he is very greedy and dishonorable since he demands people to share camps and then turns around and needs help when he cant deal with his agros. <p><BR><img src="http://faceweb-004.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/48/2329548.JPG" width=500 border=0></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ucelinaheartworthy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CelinaHeartworthy</A> at: 11/19/01 9:58:25 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ufaele.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Faele</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t d00d!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(11/19/01 1:35:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumshitlistpeopletowatchoutforonourserver.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=703.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: KSing and dishonorable monk Kanos</span><hr size=1> I'm really sorry that this happened to you, but if it makes you feel any better, you have a kick ass sig! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Faele Narsilion<Br>Uber Druish Princess of the 52nd Wandering<Br>First Officer and Consort <Br>Dogmatic Crucible<Br><Br><Br><b><i>Funny...she doesn't LOOK Druish......<b><i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF