ain. You may view this as beneath your notice, but it didn't seem to stop you from posting to defend your actions, and then making a personal attack on the poster. A typical response when a person is on shaky ground and feeling defensive about inappropriate actions. The best and safest way to avoid this type of situation is NEVER attack a mob aggro'd on another player without that player either giving explicit permission or directly asking for help.<br>Honor is in our actions, not in defending those actions.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usijandistraightarrow.showPublicProfile?language=EN>sijandistraightarrow</A> at: 11/27/01 8:40:20 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ushutshut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shut Shut</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>p0\/\/3r-p0sT3r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(11/25/01 11:48:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumshitlistpeopletowatchoutforonourserver.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=703.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.webshots.com/photos/imgs3/63/20363-small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: KSing and dishonorable monk Kanos</span><hr size=1> HUggGGS KAnos .... i know him ... hes a nice fella ....  <br>Cant we all just get along ??///???///??///???? ..... *incert slogan * MAKE LOVE NOT WAR<br><br>*ends with music * <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ujaysonn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaysonn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>p0\/\/3r-p0sT3r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(11/26/01 12:46:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumshitlistpeopletowatchoutforonourserver.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=703.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=to